data.description: Feels Brand New! Construction in 2020 by J David Custom Homes. The floor plan is well designed with 3 beds, 2.5 bath and a garage with additional parking. This home has high end finishes with Luxury vinyl flooring, custom cabinets, Quartz countertops, and the convenience of technology with the Nest thermostat. The kitchen features stainless steel appliances and opens to the living area with a gas fireplace and a Bonus room off the living area that could be office or additional Dining room. This Lake house has a covered back patio is great for grilling and entertaining. This is a perfect home for enjoying all Lake Kiowa community has to offer!
